values: so i just met my phychologist the other day she's nice and everything i just don't know if i'm going to be able to talk to her about stuff, i mean i hardly tell my friends and family stuff why would i tell her stuff when i don't even know her, when i just met her, i mean how do i know if i can trust her ya know...i don't know what she can keep secret and what she's aloud to go tell my mom, i don't wanna hurt my mom anymore so i gotta find out where the limit is of talkin to this lady. i go and see her this coming wed. at 4 i had to tell my dad about it b/c i see him on wed. and he's going to wonder why i'm going to be late and where i'm going to be...that wasn't fun telling him that.i get paid today yippy..hopefully i'll be able to get drunk this weekend with my friends b/c i was supposed to go to my dads but he's giong somewhere so i'm prob not going until sunday..so cross your fingures. so back to this lady, she wants me to keep a journal so we can go over it, and i'm like well i have one but i don't wanna talk to other ppl about it, i mean those are my personal thoughts why would i got and tell her. geez...anyways..thats all for now

it's almost been a week that i've been witht his kid and i don't think i like him like that now i mean he's nice and everything but i just don't think he's my type, i just don't feel right when i'm around him. but i dont' know how to tell him because tomorrow is homecoming and i don't want to hurt him, i mean he is a great friend and all but i think thats it, and i don't know how to tell him, i think we should just be friends.he likes me alot, i think a little to much for how long we've been goin out but thats a total different story thats not the point.....

it's funny how you think you know who your true friends are then they try to steal your identity and best friend.whats next, i mean she keeps stabbing me in the back...does she even realize what she is doing, does she realize i'm getting pissed off, i'm finally starting to get some good stuff in my life, feel like there is a reason to live. but i fee llike all of that is getting taken away from me, one after another, then i'l be back to my true depressed self doing some stuip[d shit just to make myself feel better, even if it's just for a slpit second any moment of happyness would be nice rightnow but i'm not getting any of that enstead i get a "friend" stabbing me in the back repeadidly until i'm so down there is nothing to pick me up. i don't even know if she realizes she's doing this. but she is and no one will know what it does to me, how i feel until it happens or it's over.some time i just wish i could sish all thius away to where i'd be happy with my life and not always feel like a failier, but thats all i am a depressed little child with many prob. that no one knows about because i hide it, and don't let it out. i'm just a screw-up ( it feels like) that is never goig to be good enough for anyone . i wonder if my life is ever going to get better. for a while i thogut it was. but out of all that all i got is my best friend. it's amazing how ppl; your friends can just stab you in the back. i never thought she would do this to me, but she did....thats one more reason for me to not be able to trust anyone. i've know her sinse like 2nd grade if not longer,i always expect the worsebut i never expected this....i mean this person....she's done some stupid shit to me but i never thought this, or maybe i have.i feel so alone like i can't trust anyone, but i guess that happpends when someone you thougth was a "true" friend, or close to it does something like this and stabs you in the back it's almost like she is trying to steal my identity she used to be a quiet prep ghetter girl who never more make- up and the day after i slept over she's doing everthing the same as me, wearing the same thing saying the same thing make-up the same now she's taking my crush, my ex, and tryn to get my best friend.....i don't know what to think, theres just so much shit going on, it seems like i just don't know hwo to handle it, whether to cry, be mad...i just don't know anymore, i just feel so alone...

i'm so confused my friend just tried to kiss me while i was over his house, i didn't let him, but i mean i dunno it's weird i didn't know he liked me like that, and in a way i'm starting to like the way he acts around me and twards me but i dunno if i like him like that, it's kinda like i just like the thinks he does...i dunno it's confusing but thats the story of my life, everything is confusing i'm just so lonely and i want someone to be with i just don't know if i want it to be him....
very tired, not alot on my mind just the fact i'm bored and lonely, but thats nothin new...maybe i should just give up on guys, i'm not having much luck as it is.....

my mom dyed my hair finally, it looks sweet ass! it's been a long day i'm tired....goin to try to fall asleep as i think about all the shit brendon said to me..i can't believe he said half that shit, aahhh guys piss me off! they don't even think about half the shit they say before they say it..it really does hurt!

Ahhh! i hate this school so much! omg i got a detention on like the last regular day of school all bcuz my teacher had to be a bitch and not let me go to the bathroom but she let some other chick go! so ya like i freaked out and i walked out so i got a detention. well atleast i get to serve it with jackie and christy...but i'm still pissed my mom bitched out the ass. principal for about 15 min. while i sat there and listened to all the lies he was saying to her..i swear i had to of laughed so much bcuz it's such bull crap half of it wasn't even true! grrrrr! ya obvioulsy if you didn't notice in i'm 7/8 at school so i have to make sure like no one is looking at whatever i'm typing and some girl thought it was the coolest thing that i can type without looking so ya whatever thats just gay but ne ways...ya i won't be home till like 4 today omg thats the second detention in 2 weeks and their the only 2 this year i almost make the whole year without going to smr and getting a detention and the last 2 weeks they just keep coming..i swear.
